asset_contract.name: FLUF
asset_contract.description:
This is FLUF World…

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

**Official Collections:**

[FLUF World: Thingies](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-thingies)

[FLUF World: Burrows](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-burrows)

[FLUF World: Scenes & Sounds](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-scenes-and-sounds)

name: **** The Wise
description: While flying over the Indian ocean our plane was lost in a huge storm. I was the only one of the 3 crew to survive the crash but found myself stranded on a dessert Island. With no contact to the outside world I was stranded with nothing more then a volleyball that washed up with the wreckage. As the weeks went on more items washed to shore and I was able to dress myself and throw together a little tikki bar for me and my volleyball friend, Wilson to drink at. We recently came across some speakers and an iPad nano with just 1 song which we play for the day as we wait for rescue. The drinks aren't bad and wilson is good fun but we can't wait to be rescued to a world with more of our friends. Peace.

name: Bright Eyes
description: Bright eyes, burning like fire. AKA Bigwig, an ex-officer, the largest, strongest, and bravest rabbit of the fluffle, my name in Lapine is Thlayli, which literally means Fur-head and refers to the shock of fur on the back of my head. Though I am initially harsh and cynical, I learn to show compa ssion and be less impulsive. I am cunning in my own way and with my bright eyes will always survive. How can the light that burned so brightly, suddenly burn so pale? Bright eyes.

description: This young fluffer loves the ocean and his beats. You will often catch him diving for Paua in the Southern Oceans of New Zealand. asset_contract.description:
This is FLUF World…

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

[FLUF World: Burrows](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-burrows)

name: Arnold Schwarzenfluffle
description: Young Arnold loves to show off his guns in his exclusive FLUF tank top. Contrary to popular belief, after hitting the gym, Arnold is quite the partier, giving him an astute reputation amongst his Fluf colleagues. After his arduous day in the gym, his stellar bartending skills at night make all the ladies flock to him due to his charismatic personality. Recently, he moved to the New Zealand Island of Atikutaki and is known as Maui amongst the locals. To the people on the island, he is hailed as an expert bartender and a person of superhuman strength. In his most recent bender, Arnold obtained a bull ring after drinking himself to a coma and ending up at a piercing shop at three in the morning. Now, he embraces his recent endeavor and wears it with pride to every event. Along with the nose piercing, he loves to bring his party horn and loves to add class with his golden bowtie to every event. They say you should never mix business and pleasure, but Arnold is the defining character that breaks the saying.

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle.

name: The Ex Wife
description: She was once the belle of the ball. The most beautiful Fluf you had ever seen. Tall, slim, the most incredible fur, with curves in all the right place. She was a real head turner.   She came from humble beginnings, but she was nothing but class. Her father was a musician, providing beats to Flufs on the black market who could not afford mainstream retail tunes, and her mother spent her days foraging for scraps discarded by gold jacket wearing rich Flufs who would race by in their fancy cars. There were many mouths to feed.    Growing up in this environment she was street smart. She knew how to hustle and given her genetic gift of beauty and big brain to match, she had the ability to navigate the most dangerous and dicey of situations. She was a clever Fluf.   One day, she met a boy. He was your typical Fluf from the right side of the Underground, who loved to party. His family had made their fortune in carrots, the biggest farm inside the Underground for five generations. They met at a rave in the eastern quadrant of the Underground, in the days before the great sleep. As is typical with Flufs, they fell on love quickly. They spent many days and nights racing through the Underground in his Lamborghini making all the other Flufs jealous of their fabulous lifestyle.  Eventually, he proposed and they got married. It was an extravagant, opulent affair with all the richest Fluf families attending. It was perfect.   Life was perfect. She had everything she had ever wanted.   After his parents passed away, being an only child he was left the entire family fortune. There was nothing that they could not have. For him, this was his undoing.   It was time to plan for a family. She never lost her link to her humble beginnings, she wanted many baby Flufs to make her life truly complete and provide a wonderful life for them all. As they began to plan their family, she found him to be distracted, distant, even somewhat dismissive of her. This was strange. Never before had she not been able to command his attention with a simple wiggle of her tail. Something was wrong.   Her heart was telling her she should ignore it and simply get on with having a family, but she was smart, and her head said something different.   She began to pay more attention. She would find strange gold smudges around the burrow, odd looking teeth marks on discarded half eaten carrots, and he smelled different, as if it were the scent of another Fluf on him. Her heart sunk.   After weeks of denial, she finally confronted him. Her instincts were right. He had been going behind her back and cheating on her with Cleopatra, his ex, the only pure Gold fur female in the whole of the Underground. She was heartbroken, but mostly furious.   This, is when everything changed.   As mentioned, she was clever. When getting married she had conveniently forgotten to execute her copy of their pre nup agreement as she had become quite accustomed to their lifestyle, and his permanently drunk family lawyer never chased her up. Only a couple of months before, she had been made the sole beneficiary of their assets when he had been arrested for partying too hard one too many times and the judge had threaten to freeze their assets if it happened again.   She was broken hearted, but more than that, she was out for revenge. Her anger grew every day. Her heart became impenetrable and hard. All the love she had for him turned into a deep dark hatred.   She died inside.   She cast him out, never to return, with nothing. He spends his days now wondering the Underground looking for anyone he once knew to talk about the good old days, his ramblings often causing him to be locked up for the night for public disturbance.   Now, she lives alone. A dark hearted, bitter, twisted woman who shows no signs of the once beautiful young woman who made so many heads turn. One of the richest Flufs in the Underground, she shows nothing of her wealth other than a solid gold bow tie that was once his. This acts as a reminder of his treachery, and that she must never trust again.   One day she will breed. However it will not be through love, but through a burning desire to pass on her legacy of disgust and hatred for male Flufs.   She is dead inside.   She is dark.   She is, The Ex Wife.

This is FLUF World…

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

**Official Collections:**

[FLUF World: Thingies](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-thingies)

[FLUF World: Burrows](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-burrows)

[FLUF World: Scenes & Sounds](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-scenes-and-sounds)
